name: Survive the night (itch) (Dyuman)
description:
You and your pet cat get lost in the woods you have to survive the night but there's no food so you have to use your ae to kill animals and either feed yourself or your cat you can't beat the game its an endless game and you try to get the best time you can.

I only had 24 to make the game because of some personal things I had going on.
